# UI Guidelines

- Reuse existing UI components and Tailwind tokens.
- Do not add arbitrary colors, font sizes, spacing, or shadows.
- Cover loading, empty, and error states.
- Test desktop and mobile layouts for user-facing changes.
- Check browser console and required network requests after UI work.
